@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_lfttem(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.abs((tmp + 0.91 / v2 + 0.80)) - (v1 / (v1 + 0.03 / tmp + 0.92)))
    v0 = (((v2 + 0.40 * v2 + 0.70) / (v0 + 0.40 * tmp + 0.00)) * 0.27)
    tmp = tmp
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.exp(v0))
    data[tid] = v0
